text: Hanna Hanholz (born 17 November 1987) is a German water polo player. She was part of the Germany women's national water polo team at the 2008 Women's European Water Polo Championship squads, 2010 Women's European Water Polo Championship, 2009 Women’s Water Polo World League. and 2009 World Aquatics Championships. She played for SV Blau-Weiß Bochum. == References == Category:1987 births Category:German water polo players
